translate french english3_8b8bb224:

    # "The school-day goes by normally until my English class."
    "La journée d'école se déroule normalement jusqu'à mon cours d'anglais."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:13
translate french english3_66510385:

    # "Mrs. McGee has us working on essays in class. Everyone is quiet, looking down at their papers."
    "Mme McGee nous fait rédiger des dissertations en classe. Tout le monde est silencieux, les yeux rivés sur sa feuille."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:14
translate french english3_3d0d4f25:

    # "But I feel like somebody is watching me."
    "Mais j'ai l'impression que quelqu'un m'observe."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:17
translate french english3_0ba62eb9:

    # "I look up at see Mrs. McGee gazing at me. Staring. A slight smile on her face."
    "Je lève les yeux et je vois Mme McGee qui me regarde. Elle me fixe. Un léger sourire se dessine sur son visage."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:18
translate french english3_e3525f66:

    # "I wonder what she could be thinking about?"
    "Je me demande à quoi elle peut bien penser ?"

# game/Scenes/School/English/english3.rpy:21
translate french english3_2d0786b4:

    # "She smiles, moving her hand close to her mouth."
